    *((_DWORD *)a2 + 1) = -1;
    *(_DWORD *)a2 = 0;
    *((_DWORD *)a2 + 2) = 0;
    *(_QWORD *)((char *)a2 + 12) = 0i64;
    v6 = a3;

    *a2 = 0 is the initialization of guid.
    find the modification to a2 on the following code to find the function that acquire a new guid.
    inside it there should be a virtual call on CSoundSystem.
    */
